snippet.title: Mustang Parkour

localized.description:
When @FordMustang asked us what we would do with a Mustang, we had to make our parkour fantasies come true. No question.

What would you do #inamustang? Tell us at http://www.ford.com/inamustang. 

Thanks to @FordMotorCompany for helping us to do this crazy idea! And thanks to Ronnie Shalvis for his parkour skills! 

Ronnie's Channel: https://www.youtube.com/ronniestreetstunts

Follow us on Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/warialasky
Like us on Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/warialasky

You guys ROOOOCK!!!!!

Created by Mike Brown, Landon Sperry and Casen Sperry
